## ✅ Testing Checklist

Before considering any feature complete:
1. Test in Builder (admin interface)
2. Test in Frontend (calculator display)
3. Check Vue DevTools for reactivity
4. Verify database saves correctly
5. Check network tab for API calls
6. Test after page reload (persistence)
7. Check console for errors
8. Validate TypeScript types
9. Check PHP error logs
10. Test with WordPress debug mode on

